        "text_FbG88Q": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A conventional hair dryer does one thing: it blasts hot air at your wet hair until the water evaporates. Inside OUR dryer, a built-in ion generator emits millions of negatively charged particles into the airflow. These negative ions interact directly with the water molecules clinging to your hair — which carry a positive charge.</p>",
